      "bookSlug": "luke",
      "chapterNumber": 8,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "Luke 8:9",
      "text": "ܘܫܐܠܘܗܝ ܬܠܡܝܕܘܗܝ ܕܡܢܘ ܡܬܠܐ ܗܢܐ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
